metadata.name: What a Thyme to be a Chive
metadata.description:
First piece dropped on new smart contract is this abstract of chives reaching for the light. Representing all of us in this wonderful NFT community during what it truly quite a time to be alive! Or, a chive!

I was inspired to pick this after reading [Medici Miniutes](https://www.mediciminutes.com) about [@XCOPY](https://xcopy.art/) and how they got their start on Tumblr.  I've always loved Tumblr and have posted there for years.

This post had over 1000 "notes?" and was my most popular of all time, so it makes sense to share here as #1 on the new smart contract!!!  

[5-2013](https://2stustudio.tumblr.com/post/51094315745/httpwwwcolbybrownphotographycomyour-favorite)

[8-2015](https://2stustudio.tumblr.com/post/127782159816/and-a-portrait-image-now-abstract-bokehlicious)

[5-2019](https://2stustudio.tumblr.com/post/185063075041/what-a-time-to-be-a-chive-abstract-bokeh)
